extends ../../layout

block append css
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/graphics.css')

block content
  h3 Web graphics
  p After working with Raphael.js for a bit I became interested in the different web graphics libraries, both raster and SVG based. So I thought I'd try them all out by making a number of the same small examples in each style to compare their conciseness, ease of writitng, performance and prettiness of outcome.

  p The six technologies I'll be testing out are: 

  div(class='row')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://www.w3schools.com/html/html5_canvas.asp') HTML5 canvas
        img(src='/img/graphics/HTML5.png')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://processingjs.org/') Processing.js
        img(src='/img/graphics/processingjs.jpg')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://paperjs.org/') Paper.js
        img(src='/img/graphics/paper-js.gif')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://raphaeljs.com/') Raphael.js
        img(src='/img/graphics/raphaeljs.png')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://snapsvg.io/') Snap.svg
        img(src='/img/graphics/snap.jpg')
    div(class='col', style='width: 16.6%')
      a(class='logo', href='http://keith-wood.name/svg.html') jQuery SVG
        img(src='/img/graphics/jquery.jpg')

  p Of these, canvas and Processing.js are raster based, so is Paper.js but it presents a object orientated interface, and then we have Raphael.js, Snap.svg and jQuery.svg which are SVG libraries. So clearly they do very different things and for some people not all of them may be appropriate, but what I'm doing is a fair judgement over many test cases on a moden browser to see which is more usable for me overall.

  p You can find below links to each example.

  include graphics_list

  table(class='example-table')
    each example in examples
      tr
        td
          img(src='/img/graphics/#{example.shortName}.png', class='example-img')
        td
          h3= example.longName
          p= example.description
        td
          ul
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/canvas/#{example.shortName}.html') Canvas
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/processingjs/#{example.shortName}.html') Processing.js
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/paperjs/#{example.shortName}.html') Paper.js
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/raphaeljs/#{example.shortName}.html') Raphael.js
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/snapsvg/#{example.shortName}.html') Snap.svg
            li
              a(href='/articles/graphics/jquerysvg/#{example.shortName}.html') jQuery SVG
